# RZGB Project — Cursor Rules
# Full context is in .ai-context.md — read it first before making any changes.

## Three Domains, One Codebase
- **Vrocure** (vrocure.co.uk / portal.vrocure.co.uk) — SaaS procurement platform (formerly Zaproc)
- **RZ Global Solutions** (rzglobalsolutions.co.uk) — bespoke component supply broker
- Domain detected at runtime in `src/lib/portalConfig.js` via `window.location.hostname`
- `www.vrocure.co.uk` → Vrocure landing, `portal.vrocure.co.uk` → full app, `www.rzglobalsolutions.co.uk` → RZGB landing

## Stack
- React 18 + Vite (JSX only — no TypeScript)
- Tailwind CSS (no CSS modules, no inline styles)
- Radix UI + shadcn components in `src/components/ui/`
- Lucide React for icons
- Framer Motion for animations
- Supabase for auth + database (RLS enabled, workspace_id scoped)
- React Router v6

## Import Alias
- `@/` = `src/` — always use this, never relative `../../`

## Key Files
- `src/lib/portalConfig.js` — domain routing logic (isRZGBDomain, isLandingDomain, getPortalUrl)
- `src/App.jsx` — all routes and providers
- `src/contexts/AuthContext.jsx` — useAuth() hook
- `src/pages/HomeOrRedirect.jsx` — picks landing page by domain
- `src/pages/RZGBLandingPage.jsx` — rzglobalsolutions.co.uk landing
- `src/pages/LandingPage.jsx` — vrocure.co.uk landing
- `src/components/DomainGuard.jsx` — redirects non-root paths on landing domains
- `public/.htaccess` — SPA routing on Hostinger Apache (do not delete)

## Auth Roles
super_admin > customer_admin > client > supplier
All DB queries must be scoped by workspace_id.

## Styling
- Light theme default, dark via ThemeContext toggle
- RZGB: slate + orange-500 accent, glassmorphism (backdrop-blur, bg-white/10, border-white/20)
- Zaproc: sky blue + slate, clean minimal
- Fonts: Inter (headings) + DM Sans (body) — loaded in index.html

## Git / Deploy
- `main` is protected — PRs only, Build + Lint checks must pass
- Hostinger auto-deploys all three sites from `main`
- `.env` is gitignored — set all VITE_* vars in each Hostinger site dashboard (see .env.example)
- All three sites use identical env vars — VITE_PORTAL_ORIGIN, VITE_LANDING_DOMAIN, VITE_RZGB_DOMAIN

## Do Not
- No TypeScript, no CSS files, no styled-components
- No react-icons (use lucide-react)
- No window.location.href for internal nav (use React Router)
- No new Supabase clients (use src/lib/supabase.js or supabaseAdmin.js)
- No console.log in production code
- Never commit .env or service role keys

## Critical Auth Safety Rules (DO NOT VIOLATE)
- `fetchProfileByUserId` in `authService.js` selects EXACTLY these 7 columns: `role, company_name, logo_url, is_demo, status, workspace_id, admin_scope` — **NEVER add columns or joins** — adding `onboarding_status` caused silent login failure (column may not exist on all DB instances)
- `onboarding_status` and `workspaceStatus` are loaded SEPARATELY via `fetchProfileExtras` + `fetchWorkspaceStatus` in an isolated `useEffect` in `AuthContext.jsx` — decoupled from login flow
- Supabase PostgREST embedded selects (joins) are unreliable for this schema — always use separate queries
- `fetchUserProfile` returns `'ok'|'missing'|'error'` string — `handleMissingProfile` only called on `'missing'`, never `'error'`

## Joinlist / Self-Signup System (Added 2026-03-15)
- New self-signup flow: Signup → Login → `/onboarding` (5-step wizard) → `/pending-approval` → super-admin approves → workspace active
- Workspace `status`: `pending` (new signup) → `active` (approved) | `archived` (rejected)
- Profile `onboarding_status`: `not_started` → `completed` (wizard done) → `approved` / `rejected`
- DB migration `supabase/migrations/20260319000000_joinlist.sql` **MUST be run in Supabase SQL Editor**
- `ProtectedRoute` gates pending admins: `workspaceStatus === 'pending'` → redirect `/onboarding` or `/pending-approval`
- Platform admin can approve/reject from `/platform-admin/join-requests` (`PlatformJoinlistPage`)

## Joinlist Key Files
- `src/features/onboarding/OnboardingWizard.jsx` — 5-step self-signup wizard
- `src/features/onboarding/OnboardingDetailsPanel.jsx` — read-only admin preview of onboarding data
- `src/pages/OnboardingPage.jsx` — route wrapper for wizard
- `src/pages/PendingApprovalPage.jsx` — waiting screen after wizard submit
- `src/pages/platform/PlatformJoinlistPage.jsx` — admin approve/reject UI
- `src/services/workspaceService.js` — saveOnboardingData, completeOnboarding, fetchPendingWorkspaces, approveWorkspace, rejectWorkspace

